name: Coffee Explorer - Bridge Coffee House (NORTHGATE / HALLER LAKE)
description:
We haven’t been to this location in years. It’s attached to the North Seattle Church but is its own entity. Kid-friendly, lots of parking.

NEIGHBORHOOD: Northgate near Haller Lake (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Haller_Lake,_Seattle) (west side of I-5)

ROASTER: Herkimer?

Best buses are the 345 and 346, which you can catch from the Northgate Transit Center. If you’re up for a bit of a walk, the E is also an option.

http://northseattlechurch.org/to-the-community
